{"tid":2310543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Sunnny SunMarket !! 世界級網購服務, 你值得擁有!","createTime":"2020-12-03T10:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T14:12:24.000Z","uid":197621,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69e159e58b189664fd74877e1185e203d861fdbb","tid":2310543,"uid":197621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"小弟喺Sunnny SunMarket 訂購經歷唔少, 睇番 email 紀錄, 早係2015年已經用佢哋網購, 一直都覺得好好用, 直到最近呢一次我真心屌左出嚟! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說小弟經佢哋網購 TOMMY HILFGIER 裇衫, <strong><span class=\"gold\">10月23號</span></strong>就去自取點攞衫, 返到屋企滿心歡喜打開包裝一睇. 咦喂?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 件衫嘅顏色唔對路 wo! 我訂嘅係深藍色, 收到嘅係淺藍色. 咁問佢哋前先要check下自己有冇落錯order, 費事柒出銀河系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, check 完 email, 自己冇落錯order就即刻 whatsapp 佢哋. 日子係<strong><span class=\"gold\">10月23日</span></strong>. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLaFhBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLaFhBY.png&h=9790ab31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">Email 內文, 寫明係顏色 peacoat. </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qY5eopo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqY5eopo.png&h=a5d1863d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">10月24日</span></strong>佢覆我話要 check check. 咁可能佢哋好忙啦, 我唯有<strong><span class=\"gold\">10月28日</span></strong>再問下情況啦. 點知佢哋忙到都係冇理過我. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCQxUyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCQxUyr.png&h=e5f6fedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我唯有<strong><span class=\"gold\">10月30日</span></strong>再問佢哋. 終於覆我話應該美國個邊寄錯左顏色呀,需要寄番去先做到換貨,但寄番美國嘅運費可能需要雙方負擔. 而運費係 300蚊. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻諗如果真係美國個邊寄錯左顏色, 點解會係我負責呢? 甚至係你Sunnny SunMarket負責呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我建議佢問下美國個面會唔會因應呢個情況作出補償，而唔係我同佢承擔運費. 跟住去到<strong><span class=\"gold\">11月4日</span></strong>我主動問下情況, 佢都係話要我同佢承擔運費. okay .... 咁我提出退貨退款啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rn0qvan.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRn0qvan.png&h=44f80c9e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymtrZwL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymtrZwL.png&h=e0017465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到<strong><span class=\"gold\">11月9號</span></strong>當然都係我啦, 都係我問佢哋有冇消息, 跟住<span class=\"gold\"><strong>11月10號</strong></span> 佢皇恩浩蕩咁話幫我問左公司唔可以退款, 但可以平一百蚊咁多! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬.... 唔係R你平俾我, 件衫都唔係我要嘅野, 點解要我格硬接受...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由<span class=\"gold\"><strong>11月10號</strong></span> 就完全冇覆過, 甚至連有冇其他方案都冇理過你! 你話咁優質嘅網購服務去邊到搵呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Jd0i9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Jd0i9z.png&h=e988e224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2bEzSD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2bEzSD.png&h=ee099ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後, 身為買家真係要小心, 賣家個面任何錯誤你都要硬食, 訂錯咪訂錯, 要退款? No way! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想我回覆你? No way! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗一個對大家都公平嘅方案? No way!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都收左錢就啋你都傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾百蚊事少, 但佢個處理手法真係令我嘆為觀止, 所以大家網購前真係要諗清楚啦! <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">利申: 呢幾百蚊當我係最後一次幫襯呢間黃店, 就算佢而家話可以退貨退款都不了</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7659953ead007b472a219a68295f499c52e50a7e","tid":2310543,"uid":197621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"負評嘅係sunnny員工？"},{"pid":"950c2fb642b83a3910894047aca079e3f5c2c417","tid":2310543,"uid":54854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"團購唔係應該sunnny sunmarket喺美國出貨時已經檢查咗架啦咩"},{"pid":"fd73d31ae0c780a94cd3d889e8da941ac0080dbd","tid":2310543,"uid":197621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"950c2fb642b83a3910894047aca079e3f5c2c417","tid":2310543,"uid":54854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"團購唔係應該sunnny sunmarket喺美國出貨時已經檢查咗架啦咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"真係唔知佢點運作，只係知佢將個責任轉嫁到消費者身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d50f68a52196ea2bdc5ef048ab42aa7ce8cf835","tid":2310543,"uid":85342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"用得集運lee d服務都預左係咁 賣家寄錯無得退 or 退返去既運費好貴.."},{"pid":"8d57fd5ac83f421db3be4f8b46eb6be51f81db55","tid":2310543,"uid":197621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d50f68a52196ea2bdc5ef048ab42aa7ce8cf835","tid":2310543,"uid":85342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"用得集運lee d服務都預左係咁 賣家寄錯無得退 or 退返去既運費好貴.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆呀。我都知運費好貴呀，但呢間公司勁在唯一建議係平你一百，要你接受一件你唔要嘅嘢，跟住你唔接受就完全無視你。個態度係錢已收，理閪得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa01de2bf234bb3533041863990bf9da53f8aa0","tid":2310543,"uid":54854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d50f68a52196ea2bdc5ef048ab42aa7ce8cf835","tid":2310543,"uid":85342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"用得集運lee d服務都預左係咁 賣家寄錯無得退 or 退返去既運費好貴.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"樓主好似唔係用緊集運<br />\n係用緊佢代購服務?<br />\n如果係代購 代購就有責任make sure到買家手嘅係正確產品